#

Baked Mac and Cheese with Breadcrumbs

45 min
$10
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

PastaCheesyBakedComfort Food

Description

Creamy, cheesy pasta topped with a crunchy breadcrumb layer, perfect comfort food!

Ingredients

  • elbow macaroni: 8 oz
  • cheddar cheese, shredded: 2 cups
  • milk: 2 cups
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • all-purpose flour: 1/4 cup
  • breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • mustard powder: 1 tsp
  • paprika: 1/2 tsp
